:"83f6f453c6ad0f77b91d842f21c92d73fd5b5fca","tid":781850,"uid":69071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00f37b2def77a4a36b02e08e457f2b397558f816","tid":781850,"uid":57424,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AAStocks.com.Limited/videos/1834644576622926/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAAStocks.com.Limited%2Fvideos%2F1834644576622926%2F&d=hmXJPBa3pcuiSTTUdUP3QG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9a014cd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AAStocks.com.Limited/videos/1834644576622926/</a><br />\n<br />\n真係好撚柒, 你試下美股真係抄佢家, 港獨都有計傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依個國家真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T11:21:56.000Z","msg":"美國宜家好似撚狗咁，成日都放舊肉係你咀邊，到你想食果陣又拎走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79a1361e6968fe100b6b4a4550afed0e8ac53c8","tid":781850,"uid":29248,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T11:29:09.000Z","msg":"其實侵侵做咁多野都係為咗儲氣出超必啫<br />\n<br />\n而家中美貿易戰開始觸發貨幣戰，我諗侵侵見人仔貶值夠25%就開始聯合澳洲出超必抄上海幫同四川幫嘅家，事成我六你四，肥過肥仔水。<br />\n<br />\n仲要澳洲而家係共匪最大煤輸出國，實食冇黐牙。<br />\n<br />\n維尼而家應該得返房產稅、房產權同債轉股續命，外滙燒乾之後就要再玩土地改革，但係今年佢65歲，外匯加房產可以玩4至5年，佢70，冰山都75囉，仲有魄力玩落去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}